name: Did Jesus come to bring peace on Earth

metadata.name: Де Бог? / Where is God?
metadata.description:
«ДЕ БОГ?» is the only question that comes up when you see photos of garbage bags with dead bodies inside. every day

«ДЕ БОГ?» Is the only question that sounds when you see cities wiped off the face of the earth.

«ДЕ БОГ?» - the only question that appears when you see what Russian soldiers do

«ДЕ БОГ?» = "Where is God?" in Ukrainian.

«ДЕ БОГ?» is the only question that has been on my mind for 50 days
